<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>٤٤٧٢ - حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/3651">عَبْدُ اللهِ بْنُ رَجَاءٍ، </a>حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/611">إِسْرَائِيلُ، </a>عَنْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/4851">أَبِي إِسْحَاقَ، </a>حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/895">الْبَرَاءُ </a><span class="special">﵁</span> قَالَ: <span class="c2">«غَزَوْتُ مَعَ النَّبِيِّ <span class="special">ﷺ</span> خَمْسَ عَشْرَةَ»</span>.<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>